⚙️ ENGINE DESIGN (CRITICAL)

⸻

🔹 STEP 1: Compile Config → Execution Plan

Create an ExecutionPlan:

class ExecutionStep {
    String metricName;
    MetricType type;
    AggregationType aggregationType;
    int[] inputIndexes;
}

	•	Build DAG from metric definitions
	•	Validate no cycles
	•	Perform topological sort
	•	Convert metric names → index mapping
	•	Store as ordered steps

